{
  "text": "I am just interested in the problem here that we sometimes have with transmission since the word \"others\" was used three times in the transmission rather than the word \"self. \" And could you give me an idea of the problem of communication that we had there that creates that type of an anomaly which, if I didn't catch, could create a rather large discrepancy in communication? I am Ra. Firstly, we may note the clumsiness of language and our unfamiliarity with it in our native, shall we say, experience. Secondly, we may point out that once we have miscalled or misnumbered an event or thing, that referent is quite likely to be reused for some transmission time, as you call this measurement, due to our original error having gone undetected by ourselves.",
